    <item>
      <title>Shell脚本实现ssh自动登录</title>
      <link>https://imxing.info/blog/shell-ssh-auto/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Nov 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://imxing.info/blog/shell-ssh-auto/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;root@xuxing ~&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;#yum -y install expect&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;root@xuxing ~&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# cat 123&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;#!/bin/expect&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;spawn ssh root@10.124.45.123
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;expect &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;password:&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;send &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;cisco\r&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;interact
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;root@xuxing ~&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# chmod 777 123&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;root@xuxing ~&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;#&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;root@xuxing ~&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;#&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;root@xuxing ~&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;# ./123&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;spawn ssh root@10.124.45.123
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;root@10.124.45.123&lt;span class=&#34;err&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;s password:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Last login: Fri Nov &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt; 04:53:03 &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;2020&lt;/span&gt; from 10.140.0.42
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;root@nso ~&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;#&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;root@nso ~&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;#&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;四个命令的解释 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%AA%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E5%9B%9B%E4%B8%AA%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;send：用于向进程发送字符串&lt;br&gt;
expect：从进程接收字符串&lt;br&gt;
spawn：启动新的进程&lt;br&gt;
interact：允许用户交互，如果没有该命令会直接终端 session，返回之前的终端&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
